HEADWORD: Polystome
<hw>Pol"y*stome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
many-mouthed; <grk>poly`s</grk> + <grk>sto`ma</grk> mouth.]</ety>
