==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Polystome
<hw>Pol"y*stome</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An animal
having many mouths; -- applied to Protozoa.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

